<plot>This film is a Doc-Biography of Catalan writer Josep Torrella i Pineda, and also it's the first chapter of a 'Sergi Rubió' (qv)'s project, entitled "Sabadell, bressol d'artistes": a collection of 20 Doc-Biographies of 20 artists from Sabadell, born before 1940. Nowadays, 10 years after the shooting of this documentary, the next Rubió project for the next artist comes to life, this time focusing on the Catalan painter Joaquim Montserrat i Camps.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?613607</url></doc>
